author: IGN
description:
SpongeBob SquarePants: Titans of the Tide is available now on Nintendo Switch 2, PC, PlayStation 5 (PS5), and Xbox Series X/S. Check out the SpongeBob SquarePants: Titans of the Tide launch trailer for this 3D platformer game to see gameplay and more as you help SpongeBob and Patrick save Bikini Bottom.

When the Flying Dutchman and King Neptune lock horns, their ego clash unleashes an otherworldly tidal wave across Bikini Bottom. It's up to SpongeBob and Patrick, two unlikely heroes armed with jellyfishing nets and friendship thicker than tartar sauce, to restore order to the undersea chaos.

author: IGN
description:
Dive into the complete Call of Duty: Black Ops 7 Zombies Ashes of the Damned Main Quest Easter Egg Guide, featuring a full Easter Egg walkthrough that covers every major step and secret along the way. Learn how to obtain and upgrade Old Tessie, track down the mobile Pack-a-Punch, and unlock the Necrofluid Gauntlet wonder weapon. We’ll show you all Infested Power Pump locations, explain every Serum item, and reveal the Pigpen cipher solution. You’ll also find guides for the Klaus stabilizer chip, the DG-2 turret upgrade, every Wisp step, the Zarya Cosmodrome puzzle, the Blackwater Lake projector puzzle, and a full Veytharion boss fight strategy. Everything you need to beat the Ashes of the Damned Easter Egg is right here.

description:
Lured, enslaved, and left to rust. The Alloyed Collective now stirs from the scrap of their fallen allies, driven by a singular purpose: returning home. Watch the latest Risk of Rain 2 trailer for this third-person roguelite game to see what to expect with the Alloyed Collective expansion, which features new survivors with the Drifter and Operator, new stages, new drones, new enemies, and more. Risk of Rain 2: Alloyed Collective is available now on Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, PlayStation 5 (PS5), PlayStation 4 (PS4), and PC (Epic Games Store and Steam).

description:
Resident Evil Survival Unit is out now on iOS and Android devices. Watch the Resident Evil Survival Unit launch trailer for this mobile strategy game. The new Resident Evil Survival Unit trailer showcases gameplay, iconic Resident Evil characters, and gives you a peek into its story. 

Set in a parallel world inspired by the Resident Evil universe, the game features an original storyline and real-time strategic gameplay designed for mobile platforms. author: IGN
description:
When adventurer Lara Croft (voiced by Hayley Atwell) discovers a trail of stolen African Orisha masks, she joins forces with her best friend Sam (Karen Fukuhara) to retrieve the precious artifacts. 

Lara’s thrilling new adventure takes her around the globe as she delves deeper into the hidden secrets of Orisha history, dodging the machinations of a dangerous and enigmatic billionaire who wants the masks for herself, while discovering these relics contain dark secrets and a power that defies logic. Power that may, in fact, be divine.

The voice cast includes Hayley Atwell as “Lara Croft,” Karen Fukuhara as “Sam Nishimura,” O-T Fagbenle as “Eshu,” Allen Maldonado as “Zip,” and Earl Baylon as “Jonah Maiava”.

Legendary TV is the studio behind the series. The show is executive produced and written by Tasha Huo. Additional executive producers include Story Kitchen co-founders, Dmitri M. Johnson and Mike Goldberg, along with Timothy I. Stevenson; Jacob Robinson under his company Tractor Pa
title: Tomb Raider: The Legend of Lara Croft: Season 2 Exclusive Trailer (2025) Hayley Atwell

Guild Wars Reforged is the new massive update to the 2005 beloved MMORPG; Guild Wars. 

Guild Wars Reforged is a co-development initiative between ArenaNet and partner studio 2weeks, who were formed in 2024 from former ArenaNet staff who were excited to return to the franchise after a 15-year break.

author: IGN
description:
Thanks to INNO3D and their range of Nvidia RTX 50 series cards, we have stacked the RTX 5060, RTX 5070 and RTX 5080 head to head. In a Benchmark Battlefield of Graphics, High Frame Rates, Low Latency and the best settings for each card. Using the suite of RTX features in DLSS 4, Reflex Low Latency and Multi Frame Generation to cover what spec, price and performance works best for all. In this benchmark comparison, we break down the features of each card, on high end PC specification and push each card as fast as they can go, in DICE's excellent, high performance, multiplayer hit, Battlefield 6.

Chapters
0:00 Introduction
1:22 The Cards, Specifications and Testing Methodology
2:48 Battlefield 6, Frostbite engine, Input Latency, Game Settings and baseline
3:39 RTX 5060 Best Settings and comparisons
4:40 RTX 5060 1080p DLSS Quality Performance & Latency
5:35 RTX 5060 1080p DLSS Quality 4x MFG Performance & Latency
6:58 RTX 5070 1440p DLSS Quality Performance & Latency
8:15 RTX 5070 1440
title: Battlefield 6 vs RTX 50 Series - Multiplayer Performance, Graphics & Latency Benchmarks

Don't miss the 'Rage' Featurette for Five Nights at Freddy's 2, the upcoming horror movie sequel based on the game series by Scott Cawthon, starring Josh Hutcherson, Matthew Lillard, Elizabeth Lail, and Piper Rubio. Take a look at the latest featurette as the cast details the haunting nature of the marionette in Five Nights at Freddy's 2 in theaters on December 5.

One year has passed since the supernatural nightmare at Freddy Fazbear’s Pizza. The stories about what transpired there have been twisted into a campy local legend, inspiring the town’s first ever Fazfest. 

Former security guard Mike (Josh Hutcherson) and police officer Vanessa (Elizabeth Lail) have kept the truth from Mike’s 11-year-old sister, Abby (Piper Rubio), concerning the fate of her animatronic friends.

title: Five Nights at Freddy's 2 - Official Behind the Scenes Clip (2025) Josh Hutcherson, Mckenna Grace

author: IGN
description:
Tired of walking through the modern wastelands without the convienience of a functioning PipBoy to help guide you along every step of the way? Then do we have just the contraption for you! The Wand Company, renown for their excellent crafts of prop replicas, have done it again! This time with the makings of a Vault dwellers favorite wearable companion tech, the Pip-Boy. Looking as though it was pulled straight out of the games, this Pip-Boy comes packed with UI elements from the game to track health, raditation levels, inventory management, and so much more. And, yes, it even has a fully playable version of Atomic Command. The Fallout Pip-Boy 3000 is available for pre-order now on the IGN Store. 

https://store.ign.com/products/fallout-pip-boy-3000-replica
title: Actual Functioning Pip-Boy From Fallout 3 & New Vegas
